text: The 2019 Cassis Open Provence was a professional tennis tournament played on hard courts. It was the 2nd edition of the tournament which was part of the 2019 ATP Challenger Tour. It took place in Cassis, France between 2 and 8 September 2019. ==Singles main draw entrants== ===Seeds=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! width="70"| Country ! width="175"| Player ! Rank1 !
